            <abstract>
                <p>Bartholomew James Sulivan’s address is Guildford. Please to have CD’s copy [of <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_6084.xml">Owen 1853</ref>] left at the Athenaeum Club or the Geological Society of London.</p>
                <p>He and his family are in Eastbourne but the weather has been poor.</p>
